        <p class="lesserheader">
            Discover the True Power of Prayer:
            <br>
            3 Hail Mary's every day for 9 days
        </p>
        <div class="contentfontsize">
            Worried about something? In desperate need of prayer for yourself or others? Do you want something better for your life or for your family? Do you wish to thank God for 
            special blessings you have received? Say 3 Hail Mary's without fail, everyday, for 9 days. Every day, ask Mary for your intention. Be patient, and watch Mary work wonders in your 
            life!  A NOVENA is a 9 day series of prayer. Asking Mary directly for help is considered a special type of prayer. The power of daily Hail Mary's can be seen worldwide. You don't 
            need to say an entire rosary to be heard by Mary. Start with a simple 9 day novena of 3 Hail Mary's.  
        </div>
